{
  "content": "<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How does Northern Territories business funding work?</h2>\n              <div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4\">\n                  Canada's three northern territories—Northwest Territories, Yukon, and Nunavut—operate\n                  distinct but complementary business support ecosystems. Combined, these jurisdictions\n                  invest over $125 million annually in business development, with a strong emphasis on\n                  Indigenous entrepreneurship, natural resource development, tourism, and remote\n                  community economic resilience.\n                </p>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4\">\n                  Northern business funding often comes with higher per-capita support than southern\n                  provinces due to the unique challenges of operating in remote, Arctic, and sub-Arctic\n                  environments. Programs recognize the higher costs of logistics, limited infrastructure,\n                  and shorter operating seasons that characterize northern business operations.\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-500 p-4 my-6\">\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                    <strong>Key Insight:</strong> Northern programs often provide a higher funding\n                    percentage (up to 100% for some community development projects) compared to\n                    southern equivalents. Indigenous-owned businesses and community enterprises\n                    frequently receive priority consideration.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12\">What grants are available in each territory?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\">\n                {/* NWT Business Development */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">NWT Business Development Program</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Up to $200K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>All Industries</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Comprehensive business support through the Department of Industry, Tourism\n                      and Investment. Includes startup grants, expansion funding, and sector-specific programs.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>SEED Program – up to $15K for startups</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Business Development Fund – expansion</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Tourism programs – hospitality support</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* Yukon Small Business Support */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Yukon Economic Development Programs</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Up to $150K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Yukon Focus</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Yukon Economic Development offers multiple streams including the\n                      Enterprise Trade Fund and regional development initiatives.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Enterprise Trade Fund – export support</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Dana Naye Ventures – loans up to $100K</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>YuKonstruct innovation hub</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* Nunavut Economic Development */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Nunavut Economic Development</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Up to $175K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Arctic Focus</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Nunavut Development Corporation and territorial programs focus on\n                      community-based enterprises and Inuit economic participation.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Small Business Support Program</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Community Development Fund</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Inuit-focused business programs</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* CanNor Federal */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">CanNor (Federal Northern Agency)</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Up to $500K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>All Territories</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Canadian Northern Economic Development Agency provides federal\n                      funding across all three territories with significant capacity.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Strategic Investment Program</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Inclusive Diversification – Indigenous</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Northern economic development</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Who is Eligible for Territories Business Grants?</h2>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-6\">\n                Eligibility varies by territory and program. Most require territorial residency or\n                significant northern operations. Indigenous-owned businesses often receive priority\n                and access to additional funding streams.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      Generally Eligible\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Territorial residents (minimum residency varies)</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Businesses registered in the territory</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Indigenous entrepreneurs (priority access)</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Community-based enterprises</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Projects creating territorial employment</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      Generally Ineligible\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Non-territorial residents (most programs)</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Businesses without territorial operations</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Projects already completed</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Speculative investments</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Moving southern businesses north solely for funding</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How Much Funding Can You Get in the Territories?</h2>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-6\">\n                Northern funding levels are often generous relative to project size, reflecting the\n                higher costs and strategic importance of northern economic development. Stacking\n                territorial and federal programs (CanNor) is common and encouraged.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200 mb-6\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-purple-50\">\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Territory/Program</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Typical Range</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Notes</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">NWT SEED Program</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">Up to $15K</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Startup support</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Yukon Enterprise Trade Fund</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">Up to $150K</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Export/growth</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Nunavut Small Business</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">Up to $175K</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Community business</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">CanNor (Federal)</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">Up to $500K+</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Strategic projects</td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-500 p-4\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                  <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Northern businesses should plan to stack territorial\n                  and federal funding. CanNor often provides matching or complementary funding\n                  alongside territorial programs for larger projects.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How Do You Apply for Territories Business Grants?</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-6\">\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">1</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Contact Your Territorial Office</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Start with your territorial economic development office. Staff are\n                      accessible and provide guidance on which programs fit your situation.\n                      Remote consultations by phone or video are standard.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">2</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Develop Your Business Case</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Northern programs often emphasize community impact and sustainability.\n                      Document how your business will create local employment, serve\n                      community needs, or contribute to economic diversification.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">3</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Prepare Application Materials</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Applications typically require a business plan, financial projections,\n                      and project budget. For Indigenous programs, documentation of\n                      Indigenous ownership or community connection may be required.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">4</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Submit & Review</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Northern programs often have rolling intakes and shorter review times.\n                      Expect 30-60 days for most territorial programs. CanNor may take 60-90 days.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What Documents Are Required?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center\">\n                    Core Documents\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Territorial business registration</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Proof of territorial residency</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Business plan (some provide templates)</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Financial statements or personal finance</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center\">\n                    Project-Specific\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Project budget and timeline</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Quotes from suppliers (logistics noted)</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Indigenous ownership documentation (if applicable)</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Community impact statement</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How Long Does Approval Take?</h2>\n              <div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-purple-50\">\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Program Type</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Review Timeline</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">First Payment</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Small Territorial Grants</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">2-4 weeks</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Upon approval</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Standard Programs</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">30-60 days</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Milestone basis</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">CanNor (Federal)</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">60-90 days</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Contribution agreement</td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-4\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                  <strong>Note:</strong> Northern programs generally have more flexible\n                  timelines than southern equivalents. Staff often work directly with\n                  applicants to resolve issues rather than rejecting applications outright.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What Are Common Mistakes to Avoid?</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">1</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Underestimating Northern Logistics</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          Budgets that don't account for higher northern costs\n                          (shipping, seasonal access, labor) raise red flags. Reviewers\n                          expect realistic northern pricing.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">2</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Overlooking Community Impact</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          Northern programs heavily weight community benefit. Applications\n                          focusing solely on business profit without addressing community\n                          employment or services score lower.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">3</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Not Engaging Early</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          Unlike competitive southern programs, northern offices often\n                          work collaboratively with applicants. Submitting without prior\n                          consultation misses valuable guidance.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What Indigenous business programs are available?</h2>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-6\">\n                Indigenous entrepreneurs in the territories have access to additional funding\n                streams. These programs recognize the importance of Indigenous economic\n                participation and traditional economy integration.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Aboriginal Business Canada (CanNor)</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Up to $300K for Indigenous businesses</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Youth entrepreneurship focus</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Cultural and arts enterprises</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Indigenous Loan Funds</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Dana Naye Ventures (Yukon)</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Nunavut Development Corporation</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>NWT Aboriginal Financing Fund</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Which industries get funding in the Territories?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Natural Resources</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Mining, oil and gas services, renewable energy</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Tourism & Culture</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Aurora viewing, Indigenous tourism, adventure travel</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Community Services</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Essential services, construction, logistics</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Traditional Economy</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Arts and crafts, harvesting, cultural enterprises</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">IT & Remote Work</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Telecom, IT services, remote knowledge work</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Film & Media</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Production services, northern content creation</p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What if I don't qualify for Territories grants?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">CanNor Federal Programs</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\">\n                    Federal northern agency provides substantial funding that complements\n                    territorial programs. Often used for larger projects.\n                  </p>\n                  <a href=\"/blog/canada-federal-grants\">\n                    Learn about Federal Grants →\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">Indigenous Development Corporations</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\">\n                    Many Indigenous nations and Inuit organizations operate their own\n                    business development funds and economic development programs.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                {faqData.map((faq, index) => (\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg flex items-start\">\n                        {faq.question}\n                      </h3>\n                      <p class=\"text-gray-700 mt-2 ml-7\">{faq.answer}</p>\n                  </div>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n",
  "shortAnswer": "Yes — Complete guide to Territories business grants. Access NWT Business Development, Yukon Small Business Support, Nunavut Economic Development, and Indigenous Business Programs. Funding available: up to $125M+.",
